   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>On Epeiph 21, has brought Sarmates, son of Mios, through Asatis and beasts of Mag(  ) and of P(  ), of Karanis, for the fifteenth indiction, sixty litrai of chaff, = 60 litrai, only. I, Ision, have signed.</ab>
